FLOORING MASTERY

This is a Java console app that simulates a flooring store.
Version 1.0 fulfills the basic requirements of the assignment:
- Perform basic CRUD functionality.
- Save and load from a specified file structure.
- Use Spring dependency injection to switch between a Demo and Production Mode.

Version 1.1 provides additional functionality:
- Creates an inventory for available products.
- Provides a Customer and Admin view (also using Spring dependency injection)
- Admin can add or remove flooring products and view all orders for a specified date.
